<% @page_title = "Charters" %>
<% @page_description = "Welcome" %>


<div class="full-page">

	<div class="full-menu">
		<div class="top-diag">
			<div class="inner">
				<div class="text">
					<h1>Our Charters</h1>
					<h3>Cruise through our list of charter trips. If you don't see exactly what you want to do, contact us and we will work with you to build a charter that better suits your interests!</h3>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="clearfix"></div>

		<div class="inner list">

			<div class="charter-menu color1">
				<div class="co-icon">
					<%=image_tag('dolphin.png', class: 'icon') %>
				</div>

				<div class="text">
					<h4>Sightseeing</h4>
					<div class="title-line"></div>
					<div class="clearfix"></div>

	      	<p>There are plenty of interesting things to see while on the water, including dolphins, sea turtles, beautiful homes &amp; boats.</p>
					<a class="book-btn">Book Now</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="charter-menu color2">
				<div class="co-icon">
					<%=image_tag('cocktail.png', class: 'icon') %>
				</div>

				<div class="text">
					<h4>Booze Cruises</h4>
					<div class="title-line"></div>
					<div class="clearfix"></div>

					<p>BYOB! Spend the day relaxing on the water. There are also plenty of fun restaurants &amp; bars in the area to make a quick stop for a bushwacker!</p>
					<a class="book-btn">Book Now</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="charter-menu color3">
				<div class="co-icon">
					<%=image_tag('island.png', class: 'icon') %>
				</div>

				<div class="text">
					<h4>Island Hopping</h4>
					<div class="title-line"></div>
					<div class="clearfix"></div>

					<p>The area has plenty of islands in the back bays to pull up in the boat &amp; hangout. The water is shallow &amp; calm, perfect for kids to play!</p>
					<a class="book-btn">Book Now</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="charter-menu color4">
				<div class="co-icon">
					<%=image_tag('tropical.png', class: 'icon') %>
				</div>

				<div class="text">
					<h4>Sunset Cruises</h4>
					<div class="title-line"></div>
					<div class="clearfix"></div>

					<p>This is the best time of day to be on the water! You can’t beat watching the sunset from the boat!</p>
					<a class="book-btn">Book Now</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="charter-menu color5">
				<div class="co-icon">
					<%=image_tag('jets.png', class: 'icon') %>
				</div>

				<div class="text">
					<div class="reg">
						<h4>Blue Angel Practice*</h4>
						<div class="title-line"></div>
						<div class="clearfix"></div>

						<p>This is a full day, special charter to Pensacola pass to watch the famous U.S. Navy Blue Angels practice. It is a great way to see them perform their tricks without the crowds, &amp; while hanging out at the beach!</p>
					</div>
					<div class="extra">
						<p><span class="dets">*This charter is weather dependent, &amp; available only on days the Blue Angels practice:</span> <span class="info"> April, May, July, August, September – Tuesdays &amp; Wednesdays.</span></p>
					</div>
					<!-- <a class="book-btn">Book Now</a> -->
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- <div class="celebrate-block">
			<div class="text">
				<h4>Celebrating? </h4>
