			</div>
		</div> -->
	</div>

	<div class="callout">
		<div class="inner">
			<div class="text-blk cel">
				<h4>Celebrating? </h4>
				<p>A PRIVATE boat charter is the perfect way to celebrate an anniversary, a graduation, a birthday, or anything else you might be celebrating!</p>
			</div>

			<div class="text-blk out">
				<h4>Out of town friends:</h4>
				<p>We understand that you are here to create wonderful memories with your family and friends. We want to show you the other side of Orange Beach, AL and how the locals enjoy the area by water. Let us help you have a perfect and FUN day on the water with no worries or stress!</p>
			</div>

			<div class="text-blk in">
				<h4>Locals:</h4>
				<p>We are here for you too! Have family or friends in town and want to show them a good time on the water but you do not have a boat? Or, maybe you do not want the stress of driving a boat and trying to entertain your family and friends? We can help! Give us a call today, and be sure to ask for a local’s discount!</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
